### Client Onboarding Process

**7-Step Onboarding Flow:**

```
1. DISCOVERY CALL (30-60 min)
   ├── Understand problem/opportunity
   ├── Assess technical requirements
   ├── Evaluate fit (both directions)
   └── Identify decision maker, timeline

2. PROPOSAL (1-3 days)
   ├── Executive summary
   ├── Scope of work
   ├── Deliverables with acceptance criteria
   ├── Timeline and milestones
   ├── Investment (pricing)
   └── Terms and next steps

3. CONTRACT SIGNING
   ├── MSA for new clients
   ├── SOW for project specifics
   ├── NDA if needed
   └── Digital signatures via HelloSign

4. KICKOFF MEETING (60 min)
   ├── Introductions (if multiple stakeholders)
   ├── Confirm scope and priorities
   ├── Establish communication channels
   ├── Set up access (repos, tools, environments)
   └── Schedule first milestone check-in

5. DEPOSIT/PAYMENT
   ├── 50% upfront for projects
   ├── Or first retainer payment
   └── Net-15 terms for ongoing

6. PROJECT EXECUTION
   ├── Weekly status updates
   ├── Milestone demos
   ├── Change requests via process
   └── Documentation as we go

7. PROJECT CLOSEOUT
   ├── Final delivery and acceptance
   ├── Knowledge transfer if needed
   ├── Final invoice
   ├── Request testimonial/referral
   └── Schedule follow-up check-in
```

> Sources: [Rocketlane](https://www.rocketlane.com/blogs/client-onboarding-template), [Dock](https://www.dock.us/library/client-onboarding-process)

**Key Insight:** "88% of customers are more likely to remain loyal to businesses prioritizing onboarding and education."

